title: Hammock: Eric Geiselman, Billy Stairmaid, & Perth Standlick
description:
In these days of hectic travel schedules to contests around the globe, sponsor demands, training regimes and everything else that comes with being a pro surfer, we took Eric Geiselman, Billy Stairmaid and Perth Standlick on a trip to help remind them why they started surfing: good times riding waves with their friends in a beautiful, uncluttered exotic locale.

Athletes: Eric Geiselman, Billy Stairmaid, Perth Standlick. 
Edited by: Ryan Moss
Directed by: Ryan Moss & Luke Walsh

asset.author: Oakley
